data.text:
@stefanbar @cobuspienaar @yasserogier Hi Yasser,
I would like it to pop up when the user is issued the returned case. It should show that the case was returned by a verifier and the reason it was returned by a verifier. i.e. This case was returned by a verifier as it had too many errors. Please recapture the case.

The verifier should have reasons for returning a case or possibly a text box where they can type a reason.
